- **DP on prefixes**: Extra dimension tracks the number of pairs formed
- **Non-crossing constraint**: Enforced by pairing i with p < i and using dp[p-1][t-1], which ensures all pairs lie completely to the left of p
- **Reconstruction**: Requires storing backpointers to output the actual pairs
- **Complexity**: Time O(n²k), Space O(nk)

## Code Example
