## Why This Question Is Asked

This problem evaluates proficiency in tree DP with disjoint-path packing and exact-path-count constraints, along with path reconstruction. It combines knapsack-on-tree techniques with path endpoint handling while guaranteeing vertex-disjointness.

## Key Concepts

- Tree DP with multiple states per node (unused vs. endpoint vs. interior)
